data.description: Spacious open floor plan with vaulted ceilings in main living room space!! 3 bed/2 bath split floor plan with a 12'x16' screened porch and exterior concrete pad extending the outdoor space for your BBQ.  New metal roof (only 4 years old), high impact windows replaced in 2017, and a tankless water heater.   Master bedroom is spacious with 2 separate closets and brightly updated master bathroom with double vanity.  Second and third bedrooms are ample and bright, sharing the updated second bathroom.  Has a large, open, and fully landscaped yard with sprinkler system and a well to enjoy the summer barbeques!  A must see!
